¤######---
# Catacomb Snatch
# Original by: Mojang
# Mod by: Djonn
# Help by: delvar
¤######---

Catacomb Snatch Arena is an arena version of Mojang's Catacomb Snatch.
You have to kill your enemies in order to survive, if they destroy the Holy Grail you loose.

#-- PLAYER --#
